import { Component } from '@angular/core';
import { NavController } from '@ionic/angular';


@Component({
  selector: 'app-reservas',
  templateUrl: './reservas.page.html',
  styleUrls: ['./reservas.page.scss'],
})
export class ReservasPage {

  currentDate: string;
  constructor(private navCtrl: NavController) {
    this.currentDate = new Date().toDateString();
  }


  irParaLogin() {
    this.navCtrl.navigateForward('/login');
  }

  submitReserva() {
    // Lógica para enviar a reserva

  }




}



<ion-content fullscreen class="ion-padding"> 
  <form (submit)="submitReserva()" class="reservation-form"> 
    <ion-list lines="full"> 
      <ion-item>
        <ion-label position="floating">Nome</ion-label>
        <ion-input type="text" required></ion-input>
      </ion-item>
      <ion-item>
        <ion-label position="floating">Email</ion-label>
        <ion-input type="email" required></ion-input>
      </ion-item>
      <ion-item>
        <ion-label>Número de Pessoas</ion-label>
        <ion-select interface="popover" placeholder="Selecione">
          <ion-select-option value="1">1</ion-select-option>
          <ion-select-option value="2">2</ion-select-option>
          <ion-select-option value="3">3</ion-select-option>
          <ion-select-option value="4">4</ion-select-option>
          <ion-select-option value="5">5</ion-select-option>
          <ion-select-option valueselect-option value="6">6</ion-select-option> 
        </ion-select>
      </ion-item>
      <ion-item>
        <ion-datetime presentation="date" display-format="DD/MM/YYYY" picker-format="DD MMM YYYY" 
              min="{{ currentDate }}" required></ion-datetime>

      </ion-item>
      <ion-item>
          <ion-label position="floating">Horário Preferencial</ion-label>
      </ion-item>

      <ion-radio-group> 
        <ion-item>
          <ion-label>Horário Preferencial</ion-label>
          <ion-select interface="popover" placeholder="Selecione">
            <ion-select-option *ngFor="let time of ['18:45', '19:00', '20:00', '21:00', '21:50']" value="{{ time }}">
              {{ time }}
            </ion-select-option>
          </ion-select>
        </ion-item>
        </ion-radio-group>
    </ion-list>

    <ion-button type="submit" expand="block" class="submit-button" color="danger">
      Reservar
    </ion-button>
  </form>
</ion-content>
